unittitle_ssm: Isabel May Parsons family portraits and obituaries
abstract_ssm: The collection consists of thirteen portraits of the Parsons family (circa 1910-1930s), a PS 92 class portrait (1917), and obituaries for Mary M. Parsons (circa 1920s). Mary M. Parsons was active in many Brooklyn charitable organizations. She died in Plainfield, New Jersey, in the 1920s.
